Answer -2.
mysql> select * from (select * from movie where title = 'Anand') AS m1
    -> inner join m_cast mc on mc.MID = m1.MID
    -> inner join person p on p.pid = mc.pid;
Empty set (0.13 sec)

Check Again ---
mysql> select * from m_cast mc
    -> right outer join person p on p.pid = mc.pid
    -> where mid = 'tt0066763';
Empty set (0.12 sec)


